## Example
```{r, eval=FALSE}
data2 <- ReadData(Indicator = 'Spread',
                  Index = 'New operations households')
model2 <- FitModels(data = data2, horizon=20)
plot_FitModels(model2)
```
- Best model: ARIMA$(p=1,d=1,q=1)$, where $p$ is the AR order, $d$ is the degree of differencing and $m$ is the MA order;
- Correlation: $97\%$.

